 x^2 + y^2 = 4x+4
(x-a)^2 + (y-b)^2 = r^2
(x-a)^2+(y-b)^2=r^2\implies x^2+y^2-2ax-2by+a^2+b^2-r^2=0
x^2+y^2-4x-4=0
